a. Habitus of male, lateral view, scale bar = 2.0 mm; b. Thorax, dorsal view, scale bar = 0.5 mm; c. Wing, scale bar = 1.0 mm; d. Female terminalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.2 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="66BBBFFABD47FFB4FF47F8374B6CF813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3356348/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="467" startId="12.[151,250,1968,1993]" targetBox="[249,1339,232,1907]" targetPageId="12">
<paragraph id="327BEF72BD47FFB4FF47F8374B6CF813" blockId="12.[151,1436,1968,2029]" pageId="12" pageNumber="467">
<emphasis id="00B03360BD47FFB4FF47F8374C0EF836" bold="true" box="[151,554,1968,1993]" pageId="12" pageNumber="467">
